{"tid":1631150,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"寧願你地集中搞狗屋，比人嫁禍好易嫁咋","createTime":"2019-10-06T14:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T17:47:53.000Z","uid":126142,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d770a08001cd404001f54f09675c1c3fddd158a6","tid":1631150,"uid":126142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:49:45.000Z","msg":"你想升級 過埋民主法案先"},{"pid":"118881d5b5f558b59491c52c42187d7f25cdcd02","tid":1631150,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:52:24.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"7a35b5be9f707489e016dec966101ca177570a82","tid":1631150,"uid":49184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:53:39.000Z","msg":"收皮啦，屌你老母<br />\n要圍狗屋，要送頭係你自己的事<br />\n咪撚叫人做"},{"pid":"17b79a15f5badb0dca858e7d2eb23ec472852f44","tid":1631150,"uid":126142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a35b5be9f707489e016dec966101ca177570a82","tid":1631150,"uid":49184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:53:39.000Z","msg":"收皮啦，屌你老母<br />\n要圍狗屋，要送頭係你自己的事<br />\n咪撚叫人做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:43:50.000Z","msg":"Popo出沒<br />\n搞狗屋就屌<br />\n之前已經踢爆你係五毛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c5NGBCj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc5NGBCj.png&h=d89374a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"401eab3a5116dffa8530500e84969a8d4befca33","tid":1631150,"uid":126142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:47:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o7PUWDW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo7PUWDW.png&h=3aa772e1&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}